  "title": "Junior Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><p><ul><li>Issue tax invoices, payment vouchers, cheques, and GIRO payments</li><li>Verify, process, and post payments, invoices, and journal entries into the accounting system</li><li>Review and verify monthly petty cash statements and staff claims</li><li>Maintain daily cash book schedules and monitor cash flow and balances</li><li>Perform bank reconciliations and resolve discrepancies in a timely manner</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p><p>Postgraduate Diploma or Professional Degree in Finance, Accounting, Banking, or a related discipline</p><ul><li>Minimum <strong>1 year of relevant working experience</strong></li><li>Prior experience in the construction industry will be an added advantage</li><li>Able to work independently, proactive, and a strong team player</li><li>Good time management skills with the ability to meet tight deadlines</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Interested applicants kindly click on “apply now” or send your updated resume to jayden.kua@peopleprofilers.com</p><p>Jayden Kua Jing Yu</p><p>Registration Number: R24124814</p><p>EA License Number: 02C4944</p><p>People Profilers Pte Ltd, 20 Cecil St, #08-09, PLUS Building, Singapore 049705</p><p>http://www.peopleprofilers.com</p><p></p></p>",
